# =============================================================================
# AOXCHAIN - Workspace & Multi-Crate Rust Project Template
# Standard: Security Audit, Reproducibility & Production Readiness
# =============================================================================

# --- Rust Workspace & Compilation (Global Coverage) ---
# Any 'target' folder in root or subdirectories
**/target/
# Specific build artifacts that might leak outside target
**/*.rs.bk
**/cargo-incremental/
# Compiled binaries, libraries and wasm blobs
**/*.exe
**/*.so
**/*.dylib
**/*.dll
**/*.wasm
**/*.rlib

# --- Dependency Management ---
# For Chain/Binary: We MUST keep Cargo.lock for deterministic builds.
# Only uncomment if you are building a generic library:
# Cargo.lock

# --- Environment & Sensitive Data (CRITICAL - DO NOT COMMIT) ---
# Secrets, keys and local-only configurations
**/.env
**/.env.local
**/.env.*.local
**/*.pem
**/*.key
**/*.pfx
**/*.crt
**/secrets/
**/config/local_config.toml
**/credentials.json
.local
**/.local

# --- Blockchain / Node Specifics (Data & DBs) ---
# Local database folders (RocksDB, Badger, SQLite)
**/data/
**/db/
**/ledger/
**/chain-data/
**/snapshots/
# Log files
**/*.log
**/logs/
# Local wallets and keystores
**/keystore/
**/wallets/*.json
!**/wallets/example.json

# --- Testing & Benchmarking ---
# Coverage reports (tarpaulin, grcov)
**/tarpaulin-report.html
**/coverage/
# Benchmarking (criterion)
**/target/criterion/

# --- IDEs & Editors (Clean Workspace) ---
# Visual Studio Code
**/.vscode/*
!**/.vscode/settings.json
!**/.vscode/tasks.json
!**/.vscode/launch.json
!**/.vscode/extensions.json
*.code-workspace

# JetBrains / IntelliJ / RustRover
**/.idea/
**/*.iml

# System files
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
**/*.swp
**/*~

# --- Documentation ---
# Local rustdoc output
**/target/doc/
